title: Incredible Hercules: Assault on New Olympus (Trade Paperback)
description:
The Fourth Extinction is nigh! Hera’s plot to become the
universe’s ultimate goddess has reached its final stage: With Continuum unleashed, the destruction of mankind is here! But the heroes of Earth and Olympus won’t go down without a fight! Witness Hercules’ final showdown with the nihilistic god, Typhon! Behold the evolution of Amadeus Cho into the kind of champion Athena has been grooming him to be! Watch as the combined faces of the New and Mighty Avengers race through legions of Amazon warriors! And be there as Peter Parker puts the moves on Hercules’ hot babe of a wife!
Collecting INCREDIBLE HERCULES #138-141 & ASSAULT ON NEW OLYMPUS PROLOGUE.
Rated T  …$14.99
ISBN: 978-0-7851-4546-2
